column2: SELECT     m.id, m.ra AS ra_in,    m.dec AS dec_in,     p.ObjID,     p.ra AS ra_p,     p.dec AS dec_p,    n.distance as dist,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g,     p.modelMag_r,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMag_i,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMag_z,p.modelMagErr_z,p.flags into MyDB.MyTable_NHS_out from MyDB.MyTable_NHS AS m    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN dbo.PhotoObj AS p ON n.ObjID=p.ObjID
